Privacy Policy for Text Memo Extension

This extension stores all text data locally on your device using browser storage. No personal data or saved text is ever transmitted to external servers or third parties. The only permissions requested are for the context menu (to add the right-click option) and storage (to save your text locally).

The developer does not collect, track, or have access to any information you save using this extension.

For questions or concerns, contact [your email address].

Last updated: 12-05-2025 (May 12th 2025)
